

  <div class="col-sm-12 countdown hidden-md-up">
    Support the 10th annual Elephant Charge on <span style="color: #df5409;">15 October 2017</span><br/>
    <%= (DateTime.parse('2017-10-17')-DateTime.now).to_i %> days to go
  </div>



<div class="col-sm-12" style="">
<div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" style="margin:auto;width:100%;">
  <ol class="carousel-indicators">
    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
  </ol>
  <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
    <div class="countdown countdown-float hidden-sm-down">
      Support the 10th annual Elephant Charge on <span style="color: #df5409;">15 October 2017</span><br/>
      <%= (DateTime.parse('2017-10-17')-DateTime.now).to_i %> days to go
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item active">
      <img class="d-block img-fluid carousel-img" src="<%= image_path('banners/b1.jpg')%>" alt="First slide">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
        <h3>Elephant Charge</h3>
        The <b>Elephant Charge</b> is an annual 4x4 event held in <b>Zambia</b> to raise money for conservation.
        Teams compete against each other and the Zambian bush to complete a gruelling course in the shortest distance.

      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="d-block img-fluid carousel-img" src="<%= image_path('banners/b2.jpg')%>" alt="Second slide">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
        <h3>Raising money for conservation</h3>
        The Elephant Charge is Zambia's biggest conservation fundraising event.
          Since <b>2008</b>, the Elephant Charge has raised
        <%= bold{'$' + number_with_precision(@raised,precision:0,delimiter: ',')} %> for conservation in Zambia.

      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="d-block img-fluid carousel-img" src="<%= image_path('banners/b3.jpg')%>" alt="Third slide">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
        <h3>Conserving Zambia</h3>
        Since 2008, <b><%= @teams.count %></b> Elephant Charge teams have supported
          <b><%= @grants.count %></b> grants provided to <b><%= @beneficiaries.count %></b> charities working across Zambia
          to preserve our wildlife and environment through conservation and education.

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
  </a>
  <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
  </a>
</div>
</div>

